INSERT INTO `mrc_posts` VALUES ('672', '2', '2016-10-18 07:10:26', '2016-10-18 07:10:26', 'The River Vessel (RV) Mekong Princess is a brand new boutique and luxurious river cruise vessel. Launched in 2015, she boasts twelve superbly appointed suites and a stellar hospitality crew, providing attentive service from both Vietnam and Cambodian crews.\r\n\r\nWith twelve luxurious suites, we are small, intimate boutique in style, and highly personable. At no time should our guests feel part of a ‘tour group’, we like to welcome and entertain travellers, people who have seen the World and expect a five-star travel experience.\r\n\r\nWe are the only cruise operation that commences each upstream journey from Saigon Port, located in the center of Saigon city, on the Saigon River. Access to the vessel from the central hotels is less than fifteen minutes by coach.\r\n\r\nThrough its unique engineering design and construction, RV Mekong Princess cruises with minimum engine noise and virtually no vibration and is incredibly stable in all weather and sea-state conditions.\r\n\r\nWe place much emphasis on safety. An independent specialist Singaporean based operation not only certifies our vessel, they also provide regular ongoing safety training to all sailors and service crew. Throughout the vessel, international quality safety equipment is positioned at key locations to meet every IMO (International Maritime Organization) safety drill. We boast a 100% safety record. All Viet Princess vessels are survey approved by the national Shipping Registry VIRES (Vietnam Register).', 'INNOVATIONS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'innovations', '', '', '2016-11-02 12:26:13', '2016-11-02 05:26:13', '', '0', 'https://www.vietprincess.com/?post_type=why_us&#038;p=672', '0', 'why_us', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `mrc_posts` VALUES ('673', '2', '2016-10-18 07:10:50', '2016-10-18 07:10:50', 'We have shore-based offices and attentive support staff throughout Indochina. We provide an extensive network of services to our guests, from pre-arrival in country, during your stay with us and beyond, ensuring you return home with wonderful memories of your sojourn to Southeast Asia and along the Mekong River.\r\n\r\nThrough its acclaimed human resources philosophy, Viet Princess Cruises proudly combines youthful enthusiasm onboard, with experienced senior management from Vietnam, Cambodia and Europe. This ensures that attention to detail is assured when satisfying our international passengers’s cultural and hospitality needs.', 'HOSPITALITY', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hospitality', '', '', '2016-11-02 11:57:00', '2016-11-02 04:57:00', '', '0', 'https://www.vietprincess.com/?post_type=why_us&#038;p=673', '0', 'why_us', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `mrc_posts` VALUES ('674', '2', '2016-10-18 07:11:13', '2016-10-18 07:11:13', 'We are humble, understated pioneers of river cruising in the region. We started exploring the waterways and tributaries of the Mekong back in early 2002. With more than fifteen years experiences<strong>,</strong> we proudly provide unique shore excursions and local interactions that no other cruise operation provides. We take passengers safely “off the beaten track” and to places that very few foreigners have ever visited.\r\n\r\n<strong>MR TRUONG QUANG CUONG</strong> is a Marine Engineer who graduated from the renowned Hai Phong Maritime University. He was one of the earliest pioneers in developing Mekong River cruising and was instrumental in establishing Pandaw Cruises back in 2002.\r\n\r\nHe was co-founder and CEO of Indochina Sails and was project manager for the design and construction of the accommodated cruise ship RV La Maguerite. This vessel set the benchmark standards for river cruising with its forty-six cabin French colonial style design and operation.\r\n\r\nOver the past fifteen years Mr Cuong has designed, built and operated many of the market leading cruise vessels in the region and gained a reputation for quality, innovation and safety. His credits include co-founder of Orient Cruises, co-founder of Lotus Cruises and most recently co-founder &amp; Chairman of Mekong River Cruiser Ltd – trading as Viet Princess Cruises.\r\n\r\nIn his pursuit of excellence and with a passion for all things maritime, Mr Cuong now owns two of the finest river cruises vessels on the Mekong River, namely RV Mekong Princess and RV Avalon Siem Reap.\r\n\r\nHis upcoming marine ventures include the launch of the RV Han Princess in 2017, a two hundred seat cruising restaurant for the Han River – Da Nang City.\r\n\r\n<strong>MR GIANG HOANG HAI</strong> is a vastly experienced travel &amp; tourism specialist and co-founder and Managing Director of Indochina Partner Travel (IPT). He oversees numerous offices throughout Vietnam, Cambodia and Laos. This highly regarded destination management company caters to a number of discerning travellers, including Hollywood celebrities.\r\n\r\nMr Hai’s early days were spent in senior management positions with companies such as Hoang Viet Travel, Vidotour Indochina Travel and Focus Travel Company Cambodia.\r\n\r\nHaving gained a strong reputation for his innovative and unconventional travel planning, Mr Hai now partners with some the worlds most discerning travel companies. These include Abercrombie &amp; Kent, Avalon USA and Uniworld.\r\n\r\nMost recently Mr Hai co-founded Mekong River Cruiser Ltd, the most progressive and respected Mekong River cruise operation today. Trading as Viet Princess Cruises, plans are now underway for three new vessels to meet the growing demand for the highest quality of international five star cruising.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'THE PIONEERS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-pioneers', '', '', '2016-11-21 12:24:46', '2016-11-21 05:24:46', '', '0', 'https://www.vietprincess.com/?post_type=why_us&#038;p=674', '0', 'why_us', '', '0');
