INSERT INTO `mrc_posts` VALUES ('1128', '5', '2016-11-20 23:24:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'What to expect onboard RV Mekong Princess…\n\nThis modern sleek and smartly designed river cruise vessel redefines “gliding through the waters” or “effortlessly plying the waterways of the Mekong”. Due to an innovative and quite unique engineering design, there is virtually no engine noise or vibration in any part of the public areas or guest cabins. The sensation is quite remarkable as the vessel cruises at an average speed of 8 knots (15kmh) and guests hear only the water lapping on the ships hull, or even daily life onshore, as we pass the riverbank residents going about their normal daily way of life.\n\nAny sixty-five meter river vessel is a spacious cruising platform and by design, can easily accommodate in excess of seventy guests. Founders of Mekong Rover Cruiser and Viet Cruises have stayed true to their philosophy of providing guests with a small intimate and personable space from which to truly experience and enjoy The Mekong River journeys.\n\nSeasoned Asian travellers will be familiar with the day to day language barriers that often prevent that spontaneous interaction with a local, more often concluded with a wry smile and little more. Onboard the RV Mekong Princess, your Khmer crews are all fluent English speakers and, as an added bonus, have infectious smiles and a wonderful sense of humor.', 'Life Onboard Mekong Princess', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2016-11-20 23:24:29', '2016-11-20 16:24:29', '', '0', 'https://www.vietprincess.com/?post_type=mrc_news&#038;p=1128', '0', 'mrc_news', '', '0');
